  "1901580": {
    "name": "音乐烟花秀(Music & Fireworks Show)",
    "steam_appid": 1901580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br>欢迎来到海滨城市Magnificent Bay City！在傍晚边聆听音乐，边欣赏这场美妙的自动生成的烟花秀吧！你还可以击打烟花盒释放各种颜色的烟花！<br>另外，欣赏完还可以在专属工作室编辑自定义的烟花秀！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/eca80abd0c9beb7a02ffeb7fbe91d2c6.webp?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=20 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >当前特性：</h2><strong>VR支持：</strong>支持原地范围的专属VR烟花秀观影体验。<br><br><strong>多种烟花：</strong>自动生成和展示令人眼花缭乱的各种烟花。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/2067f2d45e63e961cf52ed67408c676f.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/2067f2d45e63e961cf52ed67408c676f.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/2067f2d45e63e961cf52ed67408c676f.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>音乐高潮还有超级烟花！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/1501e629896adff1718b9bc0b6108c84.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/1501e629896adff1718b9bc0b6108c84.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/1501e629896adff1718b9bc0b6108c84.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>程序化生成烟花秀：导入你自己的音乐，核心程序会自主分析并展示契合的烟花秀。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/950975d91ba180f86c87da907901a87a.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/950975d91ba180f86c87da907901a87a.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/950975d91ba180f86c87da907901a87a.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>击打烟花盒：</strong>击打彩色烟花盒即可释放出绚烂的烟花。击打越重，释放的烟花越多！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/fcc8be1affc30efcfe145a79f142029b.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/fcc8be1affc30efcfe145a79f142029b.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/fcc8be1affc30efcfe145a79f142029b.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>激光和灯光：</strong>摆动的变色激光，以及随着节奏闪烁的灯照和绿色激光。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/353b038657ca35a5f96355ecc9d13a68.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/353b038657ca35a5f96355ecc9d13a68.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/353b038657ca35a5f96355ecc9d13a68.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>自带音乐：</strong>自带5首风格迥异的音乐供欣赏。<br><br><strong>列表播放：</strong>可以任意添加音乐到列表，后续会自动顺序展示！支持烟花秀文件或者实时生成烟花秀！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/bc7dae22f3676be8396800744cd3d271.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/bc7dae22f3676be8396800744cd3d271.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/bc7dae22f3676be8396800744cd3d271.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>观赏地点：</strong>自由选择想要观赏烟花表演的地点。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/e19cddba9c1a55f7d3d0a8263c05c1c1.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/e19cddba9c1a55f7d3d0a8263c05c1c1.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/e19cddba9c1a55f7d3d0a8263c05c1c1.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/eca80abd0c9beb7a02ffeb7fbe91d2c6.webp?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><strong>烟花秀工作室：</strong>快速编辑自己的专属烟花秀表演！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/b74ce9b1514e00923984867de31aad0c.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/b74ce9b1514e00923984867de31aad0c.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/b74ce9b1514e00923984867de31aad0c.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>选择一个已经观赏过的播放秀音乐文件，播放到你想改动的位置，在沙盘放置和移除烟花卡片就行了！<br>支持包括超级烟花在内的所有烟花类别。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发路线图：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/0f43836a49b67506be5c1f74a3ad9976.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=500 /></span><br>单音乐效果提升-&gt;互动效果提升-&gt;环境提升-&gt;性能优化 -&gt; 多音乐 -&gt; 多人游戏 -&gt; 编辑器 -&gt; Mod支持<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/eca80abd0c9beb7a02ffeb7fbe91d2c6.webp?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br>一大堆新特性正在规划和制作中，游玩过程中有任何问题欢迎在Discord频道、Steam社区或是发送邮件告诉我！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >再次感谢选择游玩music &amp; Fireworks Show!</h2></h2>",
